      "solution": "def convert_to_formatted_hex(id: int, duration_in_s: float):\n    hexa_id = str(hex(id)[2:]).upper()\n    n_digits_id = len(hexa_id)\n\n    hexa_duration = str(hex(round(duration_in_s*1000000))[2:]).upper()\n    n_digits_hexa_duration = len(hexa_duration)\n\n    return (2*2-n_digits_id)*\"0\"+hexa_id + (2*4-n_digits_hexa_duration)*\"0\"+hexa_duration\n\nn = int(input())\nfor i in range(n):\n    id, duration = input().split()\n    print(convert_to_formatted_hex(int(id),int(duration)))",
